{"ts":"2026-06-23T19:52:27.715Z","author":"claude-code-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"mergeExtensionBlueprints: pure modular composition of partial ExtensionBlueprints"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Add mergeExtensionBlueprints(...blueprints): ExtensionBlueprint to src/sdk/compose.ts — a pure, deterministic variadic merge so an author can split an extension's surface across modules/files and combine them into one blueprint for composeExtension/synthesizeExtensionManifest/preflightExtension. Merge rules: array fields (commands, preflights, itemTypes, itemFields, migrations, searchProviders, vectorStoreAdapters, importers, exporters) concatenate in order; the flags record concatenates per-command flag arrays (additive registerFlags semantics); single-handler records (commandOverrides, parsers, renderers, services) take later-blueprint-wins precedence; hooks concatenate per kind in canonical order; the imperative activate escape hatch chains in input order; deactivate chains in reverse (LIFO teardown); the manifest mirror is last-defined-wins. Returns a NEW object (never mutates inputs); zero blueprints -> {}; null/undefined fields tolerated for untyped JS authors. Duplicates surface to lintExtensionBlueprint exactly as a hand-written blueprint would."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Task"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["area:extensions","area:sdk","authoring","dx"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-06-23T19:52:27.715Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-23T19:52:27.715Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"claude-code-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-2p38"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6d